      <title>法国考虑处罚以遏制超快时尚品牌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/france-mulls-penalties-rein-ultra-fast-fashion-brands-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国占多数的议员在一项新法案中提议，对中国 Shein 等产品周转速度超快的时尚品牌应处以最高其服装售价 50% 的罚款，以抵消其对环境的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/france-mulls-penalties-rein-ultra-fast-fashion-brands-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:13:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
